<HEAD>Papers Speak Of Rail Safety Crisis After 42 Die In Three Crashes</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By MICHAEL WEST</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>LONDON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
