<TEXT>
 <PERSON> Matt </PERSON> <PERSON> Yancey </PERSON> covers <ORGANIZATION> Congress </ORGANIZATION> and was the <ORGANIZATION> AP </ORGANIZATION>'s labor writer from 1986 through 1988
